Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:36.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:40.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう言って彼女は　うつむいてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:47.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:55.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たく張り付いて凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:03:02.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}降り続く現実に傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:08.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きていく事が戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:12.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな理由だけで閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:15.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}マイハートマイストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:22.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:29.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちいさな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空がうつる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:35.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ああ鳥のように飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:47.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませたとき感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:55.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れないように　そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:36.83,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能让你忘却伤痛 我宁愿舍弃笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:40.55,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如是言语的她 默然低下了头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:47.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}任凭泪水洗刷着夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:55.06,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷漠蔓延着冻结一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:03:02.23,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛这无可喘息的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:08.80,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:12.40,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被这可悲的理由束缚着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:15.37,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My heart my story
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:22.94,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水的彼岸 那闪耀的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:29.63,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}狭小的窗口中 满眼是往昔的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:35.70,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然无法像鸟儿一样飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:47.87,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为让悲伤永远铭记于心而生的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:55.16,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了忘却而闭目哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:37.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}花は風に揺れ踊るように　雨は大地を潤すように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:42.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}この世界は寄り添い合い　生きてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:53.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}なぜ人は傷付け合うの　なぜ別れは訪れるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:59.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君が遠くに行ってもまだ　いつもこの心の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:03.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}あの優しい笑顔で埋め尽くされたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:12.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}抱きしめた君の欠片に　痛み感じてもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:16.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}繋がるから　信じてるよ　また逢えると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:23.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:29.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君の孤独を分けて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:34.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:40.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}光でも闇でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:47.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}二人だから信じ合える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:52.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}NO 離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:37.69,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}如同花朵随风起舞 如同雨水滋润大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:42.06,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}这个世界如此紧密不分 如此活泼生机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.17,0:21:53.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}却为何人们要互相伤害 为何离别会突然降临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:59.26,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即便去往遥远的地方 你总是会活在我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:03.58,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那份温柔的笑颜依旧映在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:12.74,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}拥抱着你的碎片 刺痛着我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:16.52,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}但心心相连 因为我坚信 会再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:23.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:29.23,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}多么想分担你的孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:34.53,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:40.10,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}无论身处黑暗或是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:47.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要在一起就可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.32,0:22:52.61,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永远不再分离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔的所在?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我像是知道的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说身为变革者的你也不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我知道在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们打算对维塔做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维塔原本可是为了我们使用才造出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们打算用维塔做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚制定这个计划的真意是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了即将到来的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到来的对话?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是人类的界限啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自己是万能的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明这样被抓起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我这么说呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 菲露特?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里特纳小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽她怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪打了拉塞 还把米蕾娜劫为人质…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里特纳她自称变革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽她!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有什么三长两短
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质的性命就不能保障了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同类的我和艾纽 思维是可以联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是了解的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽 之后按计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里…里特纳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们停手吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你再往前去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为只有你自己才能使用脑量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内系统被病毒感染了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵分两路 搜寻米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐到舰桥去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 艾纽在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯小姐你能来真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都把你给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C级脑量子波使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残次品超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万恶之源就是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞艾 斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算抛弃我 一走了之吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以见证世界的变革哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right 我答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为礼物 我把Cherudim也带上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间多谢你们照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真开枪啊… 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质被夺回了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为被做成女性才会被感情所左右…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽用小型艇逃脱么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这系统怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设定太随意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三闸门 自己打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后部闸门也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Cherudim和00去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向里本斯解释吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 很抱歉 要以夺回0 Raiser优先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用TRANS-AM了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算损坏这台机体吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们拥有优秀的战术预报士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser DOCKING-MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统控制权交给00了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制不能!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如洛克昂所说 离万能还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能放弃0 Raiser了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是希望能送上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一份礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser的出力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向我射击么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 艾纽!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽·里特纳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快射击啊…快给我射啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了什么待在这里的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才进入KATARON 成为天行者的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个不中用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·狄兰迪!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的觉悟只有这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔·狄兰迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的爱你的 莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你不太舒服 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子要配置新药了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔马克 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你可以抑制侵蚀你身体细胞异常的药
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你要求的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现没有纷争的世界统一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了向Gundam报双亲的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gun…dam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很看好你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台Regnant也是为了你才带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你成为人类最初的变革者 引导这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以么 露易丝·哈勒维
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 舰内系统状况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航行 战斗系统都受到了相当大的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始进行杀毒工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但完全被删除的数据量达到3456
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也有被变革者带走的数据资料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统重建所需的时间呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最短需要2210
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里特纳小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在集中精力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩 0 Riser的修理状况如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶席零件一个一个都换过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Riser系统的调整要花时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时半会儿 00可没法出击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽… 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么啊 可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会上战场的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得他们会放过这次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说该做的事情我也会做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是扣下扳机…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不得已的时候我会来做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那时候只要恨我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那里装帅了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话 没有和她战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的吧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能战斗的理由更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去进行Seravee的出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里由我来做就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你不是要操作母舰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你会不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请用Gundam来守卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E传感器有反应 从速度来看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测是敌方部队!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰艇的系统已经排不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00也已经挂彩
