Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希林格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等的目的是00的虏获哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得让那孩子帮帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶趣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勒维准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新制造的Regnant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是初次上阵 但是期待着你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam上场了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3架…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人数量不多 但是有MA在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前的类型不同么
