Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子束竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然拐弯了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这种威力是…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要中招了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想得手!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪里 艾纽!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机接近 敌机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么兴奋 莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是好男人别就这么可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是艾纽!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戏剧性的再会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深爱的女人其实是变革者 是自己的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.73,0:14:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是 赌上性命的爱情呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽引走了1架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是这边!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 这光束!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打开突破口!
