Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高浓度压缩粒子 发射!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎… 怎么会!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HYPERBURST竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢!
