Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 正在离开战斗宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00还没好么!?
