Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHIELDBIT ASSAULT-MODE!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们非得战斗!
