Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干 干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问么!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次把你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成我的女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许你说不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱… 莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的东西就要抢到手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是变革者也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下了哦 00!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 艾纽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者将领导人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是更加进化的 绝对存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人类看作是平等的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可无法忍受啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量的差距 就让你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 艾纽!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱尔… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得自己是变革者其实真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为… 为什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会遇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会在这个世界的某个地方擦肩而过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不也好么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就可以活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有你在的话就没什么活下去的动力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我们 相互理解了对方对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋… 你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋把艾纽!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙本想要回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作为变革者 而是作为人类
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我们的身边!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你这混蛋的错才!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…艾纽……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明心意相通…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和露易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音在回响…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的声音在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的… 歌声……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生道路被改变之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去血肉之亲之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链锁的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有用夺去生命来救赎么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 革新之门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.69,0:24:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 走向门的另一侧…
